item.title: Reader's Indigestion
item.description: __ Reading for God’s sake Greetings fellow reader! Yes you, you are a fellow reader! You are reading this, you can’t take it back now! Welcome to the club! We will force you to enjoy it. Also, a small clarification on the section heading, there is no God. Breaking News! Sorry you had to find out like this. Unless you know someone named God. In that case, my God!
